dct_title_s: Geological map of the Japanese Empire on the scale of 1:1,000,000
dct_alternative_sm: Central map showing the distribution of volcanoes
dct_description_sm: compiled by the Imperial Geological Survey of Japan, 1902.
"All rights reserved by Kenzaburo Azuma"--Panel on verso corner.
Includes 1 colored inset of volcanoes and 3 additional colored ancillary maps of outlying islands.
